('田阳芒果干', 'Tianyang Dried Mango', '田阳芒果干是田阳区的特产，香甜可口，便于保存。', 'Tianyang Dried Mango is a specialty of Tianyang District, sweet and easy to preserve.', '田阳芒果店', '芒果干,芒果脯', 20, '08:00-20:00', '田阳区', 106.9210, 23.7310, '13800138024', 3, 45.0, 10, 4.5, 3100, 130, '/images/food/24.jpg', NOW(), NOW()),
